---
title: Beef & Roasted Veggie Trottole with Parmesan & Parsley
description: In this dish, we've teamed the traditional Italian tomato sauce with seasoned beef mince and roasted veggies for a meal that
looks every bit as good as it tastes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-roasted-veggie-trottole-140ca530.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/beef-roasted-veggie-trottole-61886809f60321634a5b24ee-4a725368.pdf
cuisine: Italian
